Package com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.entity

Class LevelData

java.lang.Object
com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.entity.LevelData
public class LevelData extends Object
Represents dynamic loading of level data using a Factory Method Pattern.

LevelDataFactory provides a dynamic approach to initialize and retrieve level data such as layouts, supplies, and movable object ranges.
